---
// src/components/Services.astro
---
<section id="services" class="bg-crisp-grey py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mb-16 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight text-deep-black sm:text-4xl animate-fade-up">Core Infrastructure Services</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-cool-slate animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 100ms;">High-impact, zero-touch operational frameworks designed to eliminate your manual bottlenecks.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="group relative bg-pure-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-cool-slate/20 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-sharp-crimson/30 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
        <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-deep-raisin text-pure-white flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors group-hover:bg-sharp-crimson">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-deep-black mb-3">Workflow Automation</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-cool-slate leading-relaxed">Event-driven, multi-workflow processing engines linking your CRMs, databases, and communication tools.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-pure-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-cool-slate/20 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-sharp-crimson/30 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 300ms;">
        <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-deep-raisin text-pure-white flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors group-hover:bg-sharp-crimson">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-deep-black mb-3">Enterprise AI (RAG)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-cool-slate leading-relaxed">Zero-hallucination AI agents that autonomously sync policies, extract line-items, and handle internal queries.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-pure-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-cool-slate/20 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-sharp-crimson/30 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 400ms;">
        <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-deep-raisin text-pure-white flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transition-colors group-hover:bg-sharp-crimson">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-deep-black mb-3">Custom Infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-cool-slate leading-relaxed">Self-reconciling operational OS builds using cryptographic hash validation for zero duplicate files.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>